FBIS3-18052 "drweu039__a94043" FBIS-WEU-94-039-A Document Type:Daily Report 28 February 1994 ANNEX Germany Government To Establish Technology Council AU2402133194 Hamburg DPA in German 1237 GMT 24 Feb 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY AU2402133194 Hamburg DPA Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] Bonn (DPA) -- On Thursday [24 February], the Federal Cabinet decided to establish a Technology Council to make proposals for the purposeful promotion of important fields of research and technology. At the same time, it is expected to contribute to the more rapid transfer of research results into products and technological processes. Focal areas are biotechnology and genetic engineering, new materials, as well as energy, environmental, and transportation technology.
